 Empire.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aAmerican loyalistsvBiography. 0aGeneralszUnited StatesvBiography. 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / Historical.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311063899840uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030023518040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300235180423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300235180/original  a978-3-11-063899-8  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles